---
title: Garlic Haloumi & Roasted Eggplant with Plant-Based Basil Pesto & Israeli Couscous
description: This dish is packed with deep, earthy elements that are both pleasantly nutritious and satisfying. Eggplant
gets roasted with herbs until delicately fragrant and tender, then pile it onto a hearty bed of pesto infused
Israeli couscous, haloumi and root veggies. This is veggie bliss from start to finish.
